# .mailmap — committer identity normalization (Git native, root placement per Git convention)
#
# `git log --use-mailmap` and `git shortlog -sne` collapse the identities below to
# one canonical entry each. Past commit objects are immutable — this affects display
# and aggregation only, never history.
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
